headline: Trump endorses Dr. Oz for Pennsylvania Senate
author: admin
sentences: After years of Arlen Specter, Rick Santorum and Pat Toomey, looks like if a Republican wins this year in Pennsylvania it’s going to be another RINO.

#PASen pic.twitter.com/BDo6dvWhin
— Elijah Cohen (@PA_Capitol_Boy) April 9, 2022
NEW Trump endorses fellow TV star @DrOz in PA senate race.
Trump: "I have known Dr. Oz for many years, as have many others, even if only through his very successful television show."
Former President Donald Trump has endorsed Dr. Mehmet Oz for the GOP Senate primary in Pennsylvania.

— Trip Gabriel (@tripgabriel) April 9, 2022
— Holly Otterbein (@hollyotterbein) April 9, 2022
